288struct EstimationControl
289{
290 struct EnableFlags : Bitfield<EnableFlags>
291 {
292 enum _enumType : uint16_t
293 {
294 NONE = 0x0000,
295 GYRO_BIAS = 0x0001,
296 ACCEL_BIAS = 0x0002,
297 GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR = 0x0004,
298 ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR = 0x0008,
299 ANTENNA_OFFSET = 0x0010,
300 AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON = 0x0020,
301 AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON = 0x0040,
302 ALL = 0x007F,
303 };
304 uint16_t value = NONE;
305
306 EnableFlags() : value(NONE) {}
307 EnableFlags(int val) : value((uint16_t)val) {}
308 operator uint16_t() const { return value; }
309 EnableFlags& operator=(uint16_t val) { value = val; return *this; }
310 EnableFlags& operator=(int val) { value = uint16_t(val); return *this; }
311 EnableFlags& operator|=(uint16_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
312 EnableFlags& operator&=(uint16_t val) { return *this = value & val; }
313
314 bool gyroBias() const { return (value & GYRO_BIAS) > 0; }
315 void gyroBias(bool val) { if(val) value |= GYRO_BIAS; else value &= ~GYRO_BIAS; }
316 bool accelBias() const { return (value & ACCEL_BIAS) > 0; }
317 void accelBias(bool val) { if(val) value |= ACCEL_BIAS; else value &= ~ACCEL_BIAS; }
318 bool gyroScaleFactor() const { return (value & GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR) > 0; }
319 void gyroScaleFactor(bool val) { if(val) value |= GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR; else value &= ~GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR; }
320 bool accelScaleFactor() const { return (value & ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR) > 0; }
321 void accelScaleFactor(bool val) { if(val) value |= ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR; else value &= ~ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR; }
322 bool antennaOffset() const { return (value & ANTENNA_OFFSET) > 0; }
323 void antennaOffset(bool val) { if(val) value |= ANTENNA_OFFSET; else value &= ~ANTENNA_OFFSET; }
324 bool autoMagHardIron() const { return (value & AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON) > 0; }
325 void autoMagHardIron(bool val) { if(val) value |= AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON; else value &= ~AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON; }
326 bool autoMagSoftIron() const { return (value & AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON) > 0; }
327 void autoMagSoftIron(bool val) { if(val) value |= AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON; else value &= ~AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON; }
328
329 bool allSet() const { return value == ALL; }
330 void setAll() { value |= ALL; }
331 };
332
333 FunctionSelector function = static_cast<FunctionSelector>(0);
334 EnableFlags enable;
335
336 static constexpr const uint8_t DESCRIPTOR_SET = ::mip::commands_filter::DESCRIPTOR_SET;
337 static constexpr const uint8_t FIELD_DESCRIPTOR = ::mip::commands_filter::CMD_ESTIMATION_CONTROL_FLAGS;
338 static constexpr const CompositeDescriptor DESCRIPTOR = {DESCRIPTOR_SET, FIELD_DESCRIPTOR};
339 static constexpr const char* NAME = "EstimationControl";

567struct TareOrientation
568{
569 struct MipTareAxes : Bitfield<MipTareAxes>

572 {
573 NONE = 0x0,
574 ROLL = 0x1,
575 PITCH = 0x2,
576 YAW = 0x4,
577 ALL = 0x7,
578 };
579 uint8_t value = NONE;
580
581 MipTareAxes() : value(NONE) {}
582 MipTareAxes(int val) : value((uint8_t)val) {}
583 operator uint8_t() const { return value; }
584 MipTareAxes& operator=(uint8_t val) { value = val; return *this; }
585 MipTareAxes& operator=(int val) { value = uint8_t(val); return *this; }
586 MipTareAxes& operator|=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
587 MipTareAxes& operator&=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value & val; }
588
589 bool roll() const { return (value & ROLL) > 0; }
590 void roll(bool val) { if(val) value |= ROLL; else value &= ~ROLL; }
591 bool pitch() const { return (value & PITCH) > 0; }

593 bool yaw() const { return (value & YAW) > 0; }

596 bool allSet() const { return value == ALL; }

598 };

3531struct InitializationConfiguration
3532{
3533 struct AlignmentSelector : Bitfield<AlignmentSelector>
3534 {
3535 enum _enumType : uint8_t
3536 {
3537 NONE = 0x00,
3538 DUAL_ANTENNA = 0x01,
3539 KINEMATIC = 0x02,
3540 MAGNETOMETER = 0x04,
3541 EXTERNAL = 0x08,
3542 ALL = 0x0F,
3543 };
3544 uint8_t value = NONE;
3545
3546 AlignmentSelector() : value(NONE) {}
3547 AlignmentSelector(int val) : value((uint8_t)val) {}
3548 operator uint8_t() const { return value; }
3549 AlignmentSelector& operator=(uint8_t val) { value = val; return *this; }
3550 AlignmentSelector& operator=(int val) { value = uint8_t(val); return *this; }
3551 AlignmentSelector& operator|=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
3552 AlignmentSelector& operator&=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value & val; }
3553
3554 bool dualAntenna() const { return (value & DUAL_ANTENNA) > 0; }
3555 void dualAntenna(bool val) { if(val) value |= DUAL_ANTENNA; else value &= ~DUAL_ANTENNA; }
3556 bool kinematic() const { return (value & KINEMATIC) > 0; }
3557 void kinematic(bool val) { if(val) value |= KINEMATIC; else value &= ~KINEMATIC; }
3558 bool magnetometer() const { return (value & MAGNETOMETER) > 0; }
3559 void magnetometer(bool val) { if(val) value |= MAGNETOMETER; else value &= ~MAGNETOMETER; }
3560 bool external() const { return (value & EXTERNAL) > 0; }
3561 void external(bool val) { if(val) value |= EXTERNAL; else value &= ~EXTERNAL; }
3562
3563 bool allSet() const { return value == ALL; }
3564 void setAll() { value |= ALL; }
3565 };
3566

3568 {
3569 AUTO_POS_VEL_ATT = 0,

3579 float initial_heading = 0;
3580 float initial_pitch = 0;
3581 float initial_roll = 0;
3582 Vector3f initial_position;
3583 Vector3f initial_velocity;
3584 FilterReferenceFrame reference_frame_selector = static_cast<FilterReferenceFrame>(0);
3585

3594 static constexpr const uint32_t READ_PARAMS = 0x8000;
3595 static constexpr const uint32_t SAVE_PARAMS = 0x8000;
3596 static constexpr const uint32_t LOAD_PARAMS = 0x8000;
3597 static constexpr const uint32_t DEFAULT_PARAMS = 0x8000;
3598 static constexpr const uint32_t ECHOED_PARAMS = 0x0000;
3599 static constexpr const uint32_t COUNTER_PARAMS = 0x00000000;
3600
3601 auto as_tuple() const
3602 {
